    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Highways</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>parked by your eyes </l>
          <l>hating your every move </l>
          <l>feeling your hands, tasting your food </l>
          <l>can you believe that I’m not in the mood? </l>
          <l>you’re so crazy and weak </l>
          <l>and you’re a stranger to me </l>
          <l>and it’s true what they say about highways </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>can you recall the pavements on holidays? </l>
          <l>trying to be a part of your home.. </l>
          <l>when somehow you end up feeling alone </l>
          <l>and your story begins with a tear on the chin </l>
          <l>and it’s true what they say about new ways</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
